# Supabase — required for Google OAuth and Feedback storage
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR_ANON_PUBLIC_KEY

# Notes:
# 1. The EmailJS credentials for the feedback form are embedded in the
#    client (service/template/public key are meant to be public).
# 2. After setting these vars, configure the following in Supabase:
#    - Authentication → Providers → Google: enable and add OAuth client
#    - Authentication → URL Config: add your site origin to Redirect URLs
#    - Run the `feedback` table SQL (see README / task brief)
